**Message Overview**

This dashboard offers a comprehensive view of message traffic, including the geographic locations of senders, a summary of policy outcomes for DMARC, Anti-Spam, and Anti-Virus, as well as an analysis of messages by quarantine folder, disposition, and protocol. Additionally, it monitors the top 10 senders and receivers. Utilizing this data, it enhances the understanding of email traffic trends and helps in improving the email security posture.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/proofpoint_on_demand/overview)
